OL,5, A retired teacher has been charged with
OL,6, sexually assaulting a child after a BBC
OL,7, investigation revealed dozens of       
OL,8, allegations about his time at a British
OL,9, school.                                
OL,11,FDavid Price will face trial in South   
OL,12,FAfrica, where he taught after leaving  
OL,13,FEngland in the 1980s.                  
OL,15,FA former pupil in South Africa         
OL,16,Fcontacted police in December after     
OL,17,Flearning of the earlier allegations in 
OL,18,FRadio 4's In Dark Corners series.      
OL,20,FMr Price, 76, denies the charges.      
